  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b9f\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Data services may be down tomorrow?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Although the government has requested the companies providing telecommunication services to shut down data services, it has been learned that the government has abandoned this decision, saying that they are not in a position to lose that income in the current environment as data is seen as their main revenue generating segment.",
        "We have already mentioned that the Leader of the Opposition had also issued a statement in this regard. Click here to view that message.",
        "In this case, efforts may be made by the government to disable the data services tomorrow (9) in order to avoid the spread of the incidents that may take place in the protest to other parts of the country."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "tomorrow",
          "label": "DATE"
        }
      ],
